&lt;p&gt;Practice nurse required for friendly training practice in Leyton E10.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1 session per week. Day and time to be discussed.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Pay is according to qualifications, skills and experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It is essential that you hold current certificates for immunisations and cytology.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for someone who has good communication and organisational skills, the ability to use their initiative and who is an enthusiastic team player.&lt;/p&gt;
